This package includes GLSL shader code derived from Paper Shaders
(https://github.com/paper-design/shaders), Copyright Paper Design,
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
Modifications: adapted uniform names/time handling to the smoove effect
pipeline, removed the sizing/fit vertex system (plain v_uv), inlined
helper chunks, replaced the upstream noise texture with procedural
hash noise, and gated highlights by content coverage (the effect runs
over a node-scoped capture, not a full-plane surface).
